data.title: Joyce Genealogy
data.text:
On 29 Jul 1725 when Martha was 20, she married James Allen.382

On 29 Jun 1728 when Mary was 21, she married Hon. Andrew Oliver, son of Daniel Oliver & Elizabeth Belcher.382 Born on 28 Mar 1706.382 Education: Harvard 1724.

Andrew first married Mary Fitch, second Mary Sanford.
